<head>CBETA 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0723001" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0723001">〔是故如來…如來發起〕三百二十二字－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0723002" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0723002">大悲＋（元少十三法）夾註【宋】【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0723003a" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0723003a">〔間差別…法雨〕九十七字－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0723003b" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0723003b">〔善男子…聲聞果〕二百二十六字－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0724001" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0724001">飾＝餘【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
